getting us to church ever since.

01:58:54.921 --> 01:58:58.883
- I can't believe you still... fussing.
- He gonna be late to his own funeral.

01:58:59.050 --> 01:59:00.718
Are you still fussing
about Louis?

01:59:00.885 --> 01:59:03.596
He said he's gonna be here for us.

01:59:03.763 --> 01:59:07.225
- Go ahead, call him.
- I ain't calling Louis.

01:59:08.100 --> 01:59:11.062
I'm gonna get my purse and...

01:59:15.191 --> 01:59:18.486
What'd you say? Isaiah?

01:59:18.653 --> 01:59:22.198
I see you got... your mark here.

01:59:24.033 --> 01:59:26.160
I'm gonna fall all over myself.

01:59:26.327 --> 01:59:29.247
Baby, you need...
to move that to the other side.

01:59:42.635 --> 01:59:44.428
Baby?

01:59:47.181 --> 01:59:49.308
Honey?

01:59:52.144 --> 01:59:53.688
You sleeping?

01:59:57.692 --> 01:59:59.277
Baby?

02:00:01.654 --> 02:00:03.573
Are you all right?

